org.sbml.jsbml.math.parser

Interface IFormulaParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FormulaParser, FormulaParserASTNode2, FormulaParserLL3, FormulaParserLL3ASTNode2

    public interface IFormulaParser
    An interface for the FormulaParser generated by JavaCC to parse infix math formula.

    This allow users of jsbml to develop easily their own formula parser and pass it to the ASTNode.parseFormula(String, org.sbml.jsbml.text.parser.IFormulaParser) method.
